channel.description:
Hey! I'm an Animator/Editor/Compositor/Entertainer/ManGuyPerson... thing! I don't really know what the heck I'm doing so I make videos where I clearly state I have no idea what I'm doing.
-
COMMONLY ASKED QUESTIONS I GET!

Q: What program do you use to animate?
A: Flash CS6
-
Q: What kind of tablet do you have?
A: I use my mouse to animate... like one of those horrible ones you'd find at GoodWill
-
Q: When's your next video?
A: I don't have a schedule in which I regularly post. Basically if I feel like making a video I just do it. However I post updates and whatnot on my FB if you ever want to know what I'm working on.
-
Q: What program do you use to edit?
A: Sony Vegas 13
-
Q: Are you making more Pokemon videos?
A: Yes, please be patient. I am incredibly slow.
